<br>
But it doesn't work as it should.  Classes are broken.  Crafting isn't working fully yet.  Not even half the planets have even been tested AT ALL yet by the beta.<br>
<br>
*sigh*<br>
<br>
I really hope that they've got a complete and functional game client hidden away in the warehouse and that's what's been sent to production, because then I'd eat my humble pie a very VERY happy man.<br>
<br>
